      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute perfection. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or hitting the road for a weekend trip, this car is ready to go and looks fantastic doing it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
