    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is paired with a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul and the installation of rear subframe reinforcement plates to ensure structural integrity. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and chassis balance these cars are renowned for. A well-sorted enthusiast machine that prioritizes mechanical performance and analog feedback.",
      "price": 33500.0,
